# arcSecond

- _arcSecond(n)_

Answer _n_ times one _arc second_, the constant representing one sixtieth of an `arcMinute`.

```
>>> 1.arcSecond
1/648000.pi

>>> 1.arcSecond
1/60.arcMinute

>>> 1.arcSecond
1/60.square.degree
```

* * *

See also: arcMinute, degree, pi

